{"tid":52288,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[要聞]「灣仔謝霆鋒」登錄元朗主理葡國菜，為街坊提供福利","createTime":"2016-12-24T02:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T06:08:44.000Z","uid":7775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bb6342691e7d0f33ff786b23f5c6d083ea5452","tid":52288,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T02:59:15.000Z","msg":"(本報訊)年僅27歲，有「灣仔謝霆鋒」之稱的星級主廚莫迪潘於元朗開設葡式主題餐廳 Alberto's Portuguese Cafe and Bar 以饗食客，為街坊提供福利。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳雖主打高級葡國菜，唯負責人深諳香港文化，將港人忙碌、喜歡簡便的元素融入料理中。其首創「微波爐加熱法」烹調的各式美饌，有「葡萄牙波仔飯」之美譽，更完全把港、葡飲食文化融為一體。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳只佔百多平方尺的空間及十二個座位，但勝在主廚長得俊俏而有福相，風靡萬千少女慕名而來。直至餐廳光榮結業前，已錄得十七萬之毛利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95Z6051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95Z6051.jpg&h=19c93664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b67d9f882c38c0b6a9add60ed92458b8edb4023","tid":52288,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/賊喊捉賊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E8%B3%8A%E5%96%8A%E6%8D%89%E8%B3%8A&d=Obgldri6mh5%2FSbhtWCMOBhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=29bfd65b\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/賊喊捉賊</a>"},{"pid":"dc9a9bd0bd30a812ba0c5e769e9f68223bfabed0","tid":52288,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"有乜野食？"},{"pid":"1bff5c5f08a377572e423f1fa309ad94ff29a089","tid":52288,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜野食？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n葡式波仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96a3cc3862789cc3509ac57cd014a1d4b9d3163","tid":52288,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">莫生 商業奇材</span><img sr